en","target":"Author/Wanping Chen","line":104},{"title":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","target":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","line":105},{"title":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","target":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","line":106},{"title":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","target":"Author/Wan-Ping Chen","line":107},{"title":"Author/Chen Wan-Ping","target":"Author/Chen Wan-Ping","line":108},{"title":"Author/Young-Ji Shiao","target":"Author/Young-Ji Shiao","line":109},{"title":"Author/Young Ji Shiao","target":"Author/Young Ji Shiao","line":110},{"title":"Author/Chien-Chang Shen","target":"Author/Chien-Chang Shen","line":111},{"title":"Author/Chien-Chang Shen","target":"Author/Chien-Chang Shen","line":112},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/chen_erinacine_2016/chen_erinacine_2016.pdf","line":114}],"metadata":{"id":"chen_erinacine_2016","type":"article-journal","title":"Erinacine S, a Rare Sesterterpene from the Mycelia of Hericium erinaceus","issued":{"date-parts":[[2016]]},"DOI":"10.1021/acs.jnatprod.5b00474","container-title":"Journal of Natural Products","abstract":"A new sesterterpene, erinacine S, and one cyathane diterpene xyloside, erinacine A, were isolated from the ethanol extract of the mycelia of Hericium erinaceus. Their structures were elucidated by spectroscopic and X-ray analysis. A 30-day oral course of erinacines A and S attenuated Aβ plaque burden in the brains of 5-month-old female APP/PS1 transgenic mice. Moreover, erinacines A and S significantly increased the level of insulin-degrading enzyme in cerebral cortex.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Chen","given":"Chien-Chih","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chien-Chih","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chien-Chih","literal":""},{"family":"Tzeng","given":"Tsai-Teng","literal":""},{"family":"Tzeng","given":"Tsai-Teng","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""},{"family":"Chin-Chu","given":"Chen","literal":""},{"family":"Ni","given":"Ching-Li","lite